{"tid":2080302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查指香港在理財知識和能力全球排名第一","createTime":"2020-06-26T10:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T11:05:23.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd00a277ed998d8176453b1f835bee71b7c702f","tid":2080302,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"調查指香港在理財知識和能力全球排名第一<br />\n2020-06-26 HKT 15:50<br />\n<br />\n投資者及理財教育委員會公布，根據經合組織國際金融理財教育網絡一項調查，香港在26個國家及經濟體之中，理財知識和能力排名第一。<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，以21分為滿分，本港理財知識和能力分數為14.8分，其後為獲得14.7分的斯洛文尼亞，和獲得14.4分的奧地利。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534257-20200626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534257-20200626.htm&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=1edf8e8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534257-20200626.htm&h=7c658510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534257-20200626.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港人的理財知識和能力獲得肯定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"96ebf1fa89bb2c07ddf6591e95dcfe87d9357cde","tid":2080302,"uid":231480,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:29:03.000Z","msg":"姑寒縮度刻薄世界第一"},{"pid":"43cee8ea6810ea373c641e23dd998c1eb3bbb471","tid":2080302,"uid":274435,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:29:39.000Z","msg":"真啊<br />\n大個認識其他國家既人原來冇咩人會認真投資同儲蓄"},{"pid":"5d75ae8dff7a00ea875f29e10e05eb9a47713bb1","tid":2080302,"uid":277339,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"都仲係日撚日有咁多C9被人呃哂成副身家搵東張西望求救"},{"pid":"cbffa234e293bd4c77ac12ccca1661261a92587e","tid":2080302,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":